Data availability

            The datasets generated in this study are publicly available via the ICCP data server. The CESM-3Ma dataset is available at https://climatedata.ibs.re.kr/data/3ma-transient-climate-simulation (https://doi.org/10.22741/iccp.20230001)48, and the PSUIM-3Ma dataset is available at https://climatedata.ibs.re.kr/data/papers/yun-and-timmermann-2026-nature-geoscience (https://doi.org/10.22741/iccp.20260001)49.
          Code availability

            The PSUIM code is from ref. 33. The PSUIM version used in this study is available from the authors upon request. The scripts used for analysis and figure generation are publicly available via the ICCP data server at https://climatedata.ibs.re.kr/data/papers/yun-and-timmermann-2026-nature-geoscience (https://doi.org/10.22741/iccp.20260001)49.
